The '''2AS2''' was a model of sound reproduction [[Droid/Legends|droid]] used by bands across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

The droid was priced at 250 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] standard. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] musician, [[Ballifore Figg]] owned one of the units.

